My visit to Dentist for various ailments was anxious one. But Doctors were cordial and the professional way the problems handled gave me confidence to take up complete treatment. survey_response.review_text: I am V.KRISHNAN, 77 at Electronic City. I was searching for a good dental care for replacement of my dentures. I went to CROWN DENTAL CARE at KAMMASANDRA VILLAGE Road, off NEELADRI NAGAR Road, Bengalore. I was amazed at the courtesy, respect they showed. Three times, I was asked to come for measurements and I could feel the dedication and devotion in the job. It took some time for me to really understand, why they take so much time. Later I could feel the precision with which measurements are taken - even a small contour and edges are well identified and finally when the denture came and fitted, I found heavenly.  Its now over 2 months, and I feel absolutely comfortable with the fittings.   I have to place my appreciation the utmost dedication and care taken by Chief Dentist Dr.(Mrs.) SUHANYA PRASANNAKUMAR and Dr.GAYATHRI in every stage... My prarthanas that every patient coming to this CLINIC would agree and endorse my views.  My Blessings to all in the Clinic.
